            <title><![CDATA[Monster Hunter Wilds Sees Huge Jump In PC Players After Free Title Update 2]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/monster-hunter-wilds-sees-huge-jump-in-pc-players-after-free-title-update-2/1100-6532910/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
